shared_text:
SkillsUSA Massachusetts
November 11, 2019 at 12:17 AM ·

On this Veteran’s Day weekend, which also marks the 244th birthday of the United States Marine Corps, SkillsUSA Massachusetts is proud to announce the keynote speaker for our Fall State Leadership Conference!

The U.S. Marine Corps Birthday celebrates the history, memory of those who served before and rekindles the bond that unites all generations of Marines. It is a celebration of profound respect for the Marine Corps traditions and reverence to the heritage that distinguishes the Corps of Marines.

We look forward to welcoming a former State and National officer who served our organization with dedication and distinction and who now serves our Country as a United States Marine with the same dedication and distinction.
.
.
.
.
.
#veteransday #unitedstatesmarinecorps #keynotespeaker #FSLC2019 #leadersintraining #cte #championsatwork #skillsusa #imready #maskillsusa
